  "2026-07-17T06:12:23.138Z",maintainer-agent,"Fix evidence 2026-07-17: replaced idPrefix.trim().toLowerCase().replace(/-+$/, \"\") with a linear index scan trimming trailing dashes in extractReferencedPmItemIdsFromCommand (src/sdk/test/linked-command-detection.ts). Regression spec covers canonical \"PM--\" trimming, all-dash prefixes rejecting every id, a benign 64-dash decorated prefix still matching, and the pathological 50k-dash-run-plus-tail prefix that previously backtracked quadratically (pre-fix the assertion could not complete inside the suite timeout). Also extended the deps value-bearing flag set with --direction/--kind so linked-command item-reference parsing stays correct for the new flags. Alert 27 closure on the default branch to be verified after merge."
  "2026-07-17T06:16:04.041Z",codex-root,"Handoff accepted by codex-root: preserving the linear-time prefix normalization fix and completing security gates, review convergence, merge, and default-branch alert verification."
