  "2026-07-17T08:29:05.021Z",maintainer-agent,"Review follow-up evidence: removed the now-unused relationship-context counterpart parameter flagged by static analysis while retaining the linear trailing-dash linked-command scan and 50k-character regression. Exact full coverage remains 100/100/100/100. Item remains active until CodeQL alert 27 is verified closed on the merged default branch."
